ubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/china-coach-laments-most-difficult-night-after-7-0-loss-japan-2024-09-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国极宇空间发射10颗低轨卫星，瞄准星链</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/chinas-geespace-launches-10-low-orbit-satellites-eyeing-starlink-2024-09-06/</link><description>由中国汽车制造商吉利支持的公司Geespace周五表示，该公司发射了第三批卫星，作为其组建巨型星座计划的一部分，该星座被称为中国相当于美国SpaceX公司的星链。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 02:34:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/chinas-geespace-launches-10-low-orbit-satellites-eyeing-starlink-2024-09-06/</guid></item><item><title>美国关键就业数据公布前市场忐忑不安</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-09-06/</link><description>周五，亚洲股市窄幅波动，美元继续下跌，美国就业数据可能决定全球最大经济体即将降息的规模和速度，投资者对此感到提心吊胆。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 02:12:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-09-06/</guid></item><item><title>随着整合步伐加快，中国创造了价值2300亿美元的经纪业巨头</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/china-creates-230-bln-brokerage-powerhouse-consolidation-gathers-pace-2024-09-06/</link><description>分析师称，中国两家国有券商合并，打造一家资产达 2,300 亿美元的行业领军企业，是中国政府在充满挑战的市场中整合这个价值 1.7 万亿美元的行业的举措的一部分，而且这一举措将加快步伐。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 02:04:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/china-creates-230-bln-brokerage-powerhouse-consolidation-gathers-pace-2024-09-06/</guid></item><item><title>致命的超强台风“八木”袭击中国南方</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/super-typhoon-yagi-slams-southern-china-shutting-schools-cancelling-flights-2024-09-06/</link><description>周五，致命的超级台风八木带来的强风和暴雨袭击了中国南部地区，随着今年亚洲最强台风八木在海南省沿海登陆，学校连续第二天停课，航班取消。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 00:38:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/super-typhoon-yagi-slams-southern-china-shutting-schools-cancelling-flights-2024-09-06/</guid></item><item><title>早盘买盘：动荡的一周紧张结束，日元有望突破</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-09-05/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 21:51:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-09-05/</guid></item><item><title>美国和中国指挥官将在“未来几周”讨论预防冲突</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-china-commanders-discuss-conflict-prevention-in-next-few-weeks-2024-09-05/</link><description>美国驻华大使周四表示，驻印太美军司令将在未来几周内与中国武装部队南部战区司令进行通话，目的是防止超级大国之间出现任何军事误解。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 19:41:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-china-commanders-discuss-conflict-prevention-in-next-few-weeks-2024-09-05/</guid></item><item><title>万豪表示大中华区预订窗口缩短至三天以内</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/marriott-says-booking-window-greater-china-down-under-three-days-2024-09-05/</link><description>酒店运营商万豪国际集团周四表示，大中华区的一项关键预订指标目前还不到三天，在全球第二大经济体的不确定性不断上升的情况下，人们对旅行计划更加谨慎。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 16:01:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/marriott-says-booking-window-greater-china-down-under-three-days-2024-09-05/</guid></item><item><title>南非总统称中国不会将非洲推入债务陷阱</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/africa/china-is-not-pushing-africa-into-debt-trap-south-african-president-says-2024-09-05/</link><description>南非总统西里尔·拉马福萨周四表示，他不认为中国在非洲的投资会将非洲大陆推入“债务陷阱”，而是互利关系的一部分。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 14:00:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/africa/china-is-not-pushing-africa-into-debt-trap-south-african-president-says-2024-09-05/</guid></item><item><title>《资本》报道，德国正在起草针对中国在线折扣店的法规</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/germany-drafting-regulations-chinese-online-discounters-capital-reports-2024-09-05/</link><description>据《资本》杂志报道，德国正在起草新法规，以确保 Temu 和 Shein 等中国折扣零售商遵守产品安全、环境保护、消费者权利以及海关和税法标准。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 11:06:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/germany-drafting-regulations-chinese-online-discounters-capital-reports-2024-09-05/</guid></item><item><title>特斯拉股价因计划在欧洲和中国推出全自动驾驶而上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-shares-gain-plans-launch-full-self-driving-europe-china-2024-09-05/</link><description>特斯拉股价周四上涨逾 6%，此前这家电动汽车制造商坚持其在中国和欧洲推出全自动驾驶 (FSD) 高级驾驶员辅助软件的计划，等待监管机构的批准。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 10:37:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-shares-gain-plans-launch-full-self-driving-europe-china-2024-09-05/</guid></item><item><title>摩根大通以“关税战2.0”风险为由放弃购买中国股票的呼吁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/jpmorgan-ditches-call-buy-chinese-stocks-citing-tariff-war-20-risk-2024-09-05/</link><description>摩根大通放弃了对中国股票的买入建议，警告 11 月美国大选后可能出现第二次关税战的风险，并对中国经济增长表示担忧。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 08:53:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/jpmorgan-ditches-call-buy-chinese-stocks-citing-tariff-war-20-risk-2024-09-05/</guid></item></channel></rss>